description:
As our Advent Program reaches its crescendo, it is our absolute pleasure to invite our community and friends to participate in our Charity Auction. All proceeds from the auction will be donated to a charity that focuses on children's needs, as voted on by our community in week 1 of Advent.

The winner of the auction will be gifted...

 1 Luxury apartment on the 69th floor (item being bid on), 
 1 Standard apartment on the 69th floor, 
 1 Airdropped ZenAcademy Genesis NFT, 
 1 Airdropped Roaring Leaders NFT, 
 1 Airdropped Broadcasters NFT, 
 Special discord role highlighting charitable contributions

Apprx $15,000 in value
name: Apt #21 - Floor #69 - Tower #1
